INSERT INTO execution_process_log_entries (
                       execution_id, channel, entry_index, entry_json
                   ) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)
                   ON CONFLICT(execution_id, channel, entry_index)
                   DO UPDATE SET
                     entry_json = excluded.entry_json,
                     updated_at = datetime('now', 'subsec')
